#

Sloppy Joe Tacos

30 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinKid-FriendlyQuick Meal

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

AmericanTacosEasy Meal

Description

A fun twist on classic Sloppy Joes, these tacos are packed with savory ground beef and a tangy sauce, all wrapped in a soft tortilla!

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • taco shells: 8
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • ketchup: 1/2 cup
  • mustard: 1 tbsp
  • brown sugar: 1 tbsp
  • worcestershire sauce: 1 tbsp
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • lettuce: 1 cup, shredded
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • pickles: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
